"ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016988, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In his book Mibah, Allama Hilli says: This Istekhara has been narrated from Imam Mahdi (A.S.) in the following way: Recite <Surah Fateha> 10 times or 3 times or once, then recite <Surah Qadr> 10 times, then recite the following supplication thrice…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allama Hilli kitaab Misbah mein farmate hai yeh tareeqa Hazrat Baqiyyatulla Al-Aazam se riwaayat huwa hai. 10 ya 3 ya 1 martaba <Surah Fateha> aur <Surah Qadr> 10 martaba padhe is ke baad yeh dua 3 martaba padhe…", "UrduDescription": "علامہ حلی نے کتاب مصباح میں کہا ہے کہ اس استخارہ کی آخری حجت کی طرف سے روایت ہوئی ہے اور اس کا طریقہ اس طرح ہے کہ <سورۂ فاتحہ> کو ۱۰ دفعہ یا ۳ دفعہ یا ایک دفعہ پڑھے اس کے بعد <سورۂ قدر> کو بھی ۱۰ مرتبہ پڑھے اس کے بعد ۳ مرتبہ یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "Arabic