 "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016989, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, I seek the good from You because You know about the fate of all affairs, I seek advice from You because I am optimistic about You for all that I desire and all that I fear. O Allah, if that affair (and name your work) is attached to Your grace from the beginning till the end, and is enveloped by Your blessings throughout its days and nights, then select it for me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khudaaya! Mai Tujh se talab'e khair kar raha hu kyu’n keh Tu umoor ke awaaqib o nataaej se waaqif hai aur Tujh se mashwarah kar raha hu, kyu’n keh jin cheezo’n ki mujhe ummeed hai aur jin se khouf-zadah hu unke baare mein Tujh se husne-zan rakhta hu.", "Urdu": "خدایا! میں تجھ سے طلبِ خیر کر رہا ہوں کیوں کہ تو امور کے عواقب و نتائج سے واقف ہے اور تجھ سے مشورہ کر رہا ہوں کیوں کہ جن چیزوں کی مجھے امید ہے اور جن سے خوف زدہ ہوں ان کے بارے میں میں تجھ سے حُسن ظن رکھتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْتَخِیْرُكَ لِعِلْمِكَ بِعَاقِبَۃِ الْاُمُوْرِ، وَاَسْتَشِیْرُكَ لِحُسْنِ ظَنِّیْ بِكَ فِی الْمَامُوْلِ وَالْمَحْذُوْرِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنْ كَانَ الْاَمْرُ الْفَلَانِیْ بِمَا قَدْ نِیْطَتْ بِالْبَرَكَۃِ اَعْجَازُهٗ وَبَوَادِیْهٖ، وَحُفَّتْ بِالْكَرَامَۃِ اَیَّامُهٗ وَلَیَالِیْهِ، فَخِرْلِیَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016990, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, such that its rebellion calms down, and it possesses happy and prosperous days. O Allah, if You will command I will perform it, and if You forbid me from it, I will forsake it. O Allah, indeed I seek the good from You through Your Mercy, the good along with the welfare.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baare-Ilaaha! Is fula’n kaam ka aaghaaz o anjaam agar barkato’n ke ham-raah hai aur uske shab o roz karaamat o sharaafat ke haamil ho to mere liye us mein aisi khair o bhalaayi ka intekhaab farma jo sakhtiyo’n ko aasaa-isho’n (aasaani) mein badal de aur uske dino ko nishaat (khushi) o suroor se pur kar de. Khudaaya! Agar Tera hukm ho to baja laawunga aur agar Tu mana farmaye to ruk jaawunga. Khudaaya! Teri rehmat ke saath Tujh se khair o aafiyat ka taalib hu.", "Urdu": "بارِ الہٰا! اس فلاں کام کا آغاز و انجام اگر برکتوں کے ہمراہ ہے اور اس کے شب و روز کرامت و شرافت کے حامل ہوں تو میرے لئے اس میں ایسی خیر و بھلائی کا انتخاب فرما جو سختیوں کو آسائشوں میں بدل دے اور اس کے دنوں کو نشاط و سرور سے پُر کر دے۔ خدایا! اگر تیرا حکم ہو تو بجالاؤں گا اور اگر تو منع فرمائے تو رک جاؤں گا۔ خدایا! تیری رحمت کے ساتھ تجھ سے خیر و عافیت کا طالب ہوں۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فِیْهٖ خِیَرَۃً تَرُدُّ شَمُوْسَهٗ ذَلُوْلًا، وَتَقْعَضُ اَیَّامَهٗ سُرُوْرًا۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِمَّا اَمْرٌ فَاَئْتَمِرُ، اِمَّانَهْیٌ فَاَنْتَهِهْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْتَخِیْرُكَ بِرَحْمَتِكَ خِیَرَۃً فِیْ عَافِیَۃٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": n